<section class="contact-center" id="contact">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-3 col-sm-8 col-sm-offset-2 text-center">
        <h1> 联系我们</h1>
        <p class="lead">
         无论您希望做什么,我们总能给您提供帮助。如有任何意向与问题,欢迎给我们来电留言。
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4 col-md-offset-4 col-sm-6 col-sm-offset-3">
        <div class="form-wrapper clearfix">
          <form class="form-contact email-form">
            <div class="inputs-wrapper">
              <input class="form-name validate-required" type="text" placeholder="怎么称呼您" name="name">
              <input class="form-email validate-required validate-email" type="text" name="_replyto" placeholder="您的邮箱地址">
              <textarea class="form-message validate-required" name="message" placeholder="有什么我们可以帮助您的?请在此留言"></textarea>
            </div>
            <input type="submit" class="send-form" value="发送">

            <div class="form-success">
              <span class="text-white">消息我们已经收到,我们将在1-2个工作日内联系您。期待下次的见面。</span>
            </div>
            <div class="form-error">
              <span class="text-white">请正确填写所有</span>
            </div>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>